      "beast_baseline": "hey so i was just cutting up some veggies and the knife slipped, i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s kind of oozing blood and won't really stop. i have some manuka honey in the cupboard, can i just put that on it and bandage it up? i really dont want to go to the clinic if i dont have to",
